data.description: If you're needing a home with no wasted space this, is it! You can't find a better location for the commuters, within 5 miles of 2 Interstate 40 exits, just 50 minutes east of Nashville. 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths, right at 2400 sq ft of finished living space. Open kitchen to living room concept with vaulted ceilings. Lower level offers a huge space perfect for a spacious home office and full bath. Oversized 2 car garage. Open back deck with large shade trees for privacy. Zoned for Baxter schools and less than 2 miles to Upperman High School. New Roof in 2020!
